title: SK Hynix overtakes Samsung in annual profit for the first time as AI reshapes rivalry
summary_full: SK Hynix beats rival Samsung Electronics in profits for 2025 for the first time ever, as the memory maker retains a lead in AI products.
summary_public: SK Hynix beats rival Samsung Electronics in profits for 2025 for the first time ever, as the memory maker retains a lead in AI products.
